&lt;p&gt;You have a syntax error in your function declaration (missing parenthesis):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;default s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; getContent {
